Class SmallRingDescriptor

    • org.openscience.cdk.qsar.descriptors.molecular.SmallRingDescriptor

    @TestClass(value="org.openscience.cdk.qsar.descriptors.molecular.SmallRingDescriptorTest")
public class SmallRingDescriptor
extends Object
implements IMolecularDescriptor
    Small ring descriptors: these are based on enumeration of all the small rings (sizes 3 to 9) in a molecule, which can be obtained quickly and deterministically.
